---
title: Sesame Beef Stir Fry with Broccoli and Yakisoba Noodles
description: Traditional beef stir-fry is great, but this garlic, ginger, and sweet chili concoction is seriously mind-blowing.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sesame-beef-stir-fry-18aa9693.jpg
